  "text": "It turns out that randomized QMC quadratures based on pairwise negatively dependent sampling schemes may lead to variance reduction in comparison to the simple MC quadratures. Here we describe shortly one of such cases, namely when integrands are bounded quasimonotone functions. The following exposition is based on [CITATION_1] .",
